data.description: Gracious Galloway Gardens home in East Memphis tucked away on a lush landscaped site. Immaculate hardwood floors with smooth ceilings in most rooms. Main BR has ensuite bath. Eat-in kitchen w/ granite counters, stainless appliances & custom cabs. Beautiful large open family room with large fireplace for holiday gatherings and inviting back yard space for relaxing. Painted brick exterior, 2 car detached garage w/workshop studio / space. Perm. staircase to floored attic to hold all your treasures.
